15,01Christmas, every smiling child's dream
15,01of sugarplums and smiling Elmo's glee.
15,01The gifts from Santa come without a fee
15,01but parents slowly peter out of steam.

15,01Boxing day - the only recompense
15,01to weeks of frantic shopping here and there.
15,01It justifies grey streaking in tehir hair.
15,01Still more unwanted stuff - at less expense!

